Extraction: to  transfer all or a substantial part of the data of a database to another medium by any means or in any form, in a permanent or temporary way;
Re-utilization: to make available to the public all or a substantial part of the data of a database by the distribution of copies, by renting, by on-line or other forms of transmission.
